Steps Involved:
• Data Collection: Gathered state-wise Electric Vehicle (EV) sales data from reliable sources.
• Data Cleaning: Removed duplicate records, corrected errors, handled missing values, and
standardized formats using Excel.
• Data Preparation: Organized the cleaned dataset by states, years, and categories to
make it ready for visualization.
• Data Import: Imported the prepared data into Power BI for further analysis.
• Data Modeling: Created relationships, calculated totals, and added new measures to
enable deeper insights.
• Visualization: Designed an interactive Power BI dashboard with maps, charts, tables, and
filters to display sales trends, state-wise comparisons, and adoption patterns.
